subject: Videos Are Up
author: Steve Hultay
full_text:
I posted some videos on my site with some samples of the different 
boxes i use and what they each sound like.  I tried using youtube, but 
their site went down.  Here's the link

http://www.keyportparanormal.com/ghostboxsamplevideos.html

If you can't get there from the link, just go to keyportparanormal.com 
and click on Ghost Box Sample Videos

-Steve H.

I have many boxes, so more videos to follow.  Just something for the 
newcomers to expect each to sound like.
